<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Jian Guo - Software Engineer & Researcher">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Biography</h2>
      <p>
        I am currently a Software Development Engineer at Huawei Cloud.
        I received my Ph.D. from Huazhong University of Science and Technology (HUST) in 2017, advised by Prof. Fangming Liu,
        and my B.E. from HUST in 2011.
      </p>
      <p>
        My research centers on datacenter networking — bandwidth allocation, scheduling, and software-defined networking.
        I published at top venues including USENIX ATC, IEEE INFOCOM, IEEE ICNP, IEEE ICDCS, and IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking.
      </p>

      <h2>Publications</h2>

